StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetCandidateAsvab]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
(@PersonID INT ,@Version VARCHAR(3) ,@Date DATETIME) AS
SELECT 1 AS ID, MARINE_CANDIDATE_ID, ASVAB_DATE, 'ASVAB' AS EXAM_TYPE, VERSION, AFQT_SCORE, GS_SUBTEST, AR_SUBTEST, WK_SUBTEST, PC_SUBTEST, NO_SUBTEST, CS_SUBTEST, AS_SUBTEST, MK_SUBTEST, MC_SUBTEST, EI_SUBTEST, VE_SUBTEST, AO_SUBTEST, GT_SCORE, EL_SCORE, CL_SCORE, MM_SCORE, MEPS_ORGANIZATION_ID, RETEST_ELIGIBILITY_DATE FROM [dbo].[CANDIDATE_ASVAB] WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE MARINE_CANDIDATE_ID = @PersonID AND VERSION = @Version AND ASVAB_DATE = @Date
